_sText:
This is my second map, my first was a simple Gungame map. I've Been working on this one by myself for a little while now, and I'm glad that I have something I can finally release.

This is the first release, with more to come. There has been absolutely no testing so far. So let me know of any severe imbalances.
Known Bugs:

-Outside platform turns black when in spectator.

Please leave feedback and bug reports.
